Yeah, it's an electric horn. They've got air horns that do the same 
thing as well...and they're much nicer...and more expensive. Mine's 
cheesy, but effective.

I've got a big red button mounted on the dash in place of the ash 
tray. I had the button in my stash and it just seemed right.
